{"tid":1034390,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[港女廚房]正宗韓式料理","createTime":"2019-02-23T22:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T14:57:20.000Z","uid":96525,"like":13,"dislike":143,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"9d7e0a5315a4399542cc7ae8761a982053e2b7f7","tid":1034390,"uid":96525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T22:40:23.000Z","msg":"韓國身為東亞最尾機國家，飲食文化當然好好值得我地學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日我就教大家我嘅畢生絕學正宗韓國料理，特別係絲打，點樣俘虜老公/男朋友個胃！<br />\n<br />\n唔知韓國點樣尾機法可以睇咗呢個post先<br />\n<br />\n韓國真係一個好尾機既國家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1021038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1021038</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n材料：韓式拉麵，雞蛋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DqJaTMP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDqJaTMP.png&h=965e46e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrYNV0a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyrYNV0a.png&h=1524fd80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個麵餅睇落好有誠意！韓國真係屈到！<br />\n<br />\n首先加550ml水（我用量杯）<br />\n<br />\n水滾後放入麵餅，調味料，煮5分鐘<br />\n<br />\n喺4分鐘嗰陣打隻蛋落去！大功告成！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQz9pTv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQz9pTv.png&h=0b9beeb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去過韓國旅行嘅人都知道，幾乎每間餐廳都會有伴菜提供（呢個都係韓國飲食文化其中一個屈機之處👍🏿）<br />\n話明正宗韓式料理，當然唔少得伴菜！呢個係辣八爪魚嚟！（我真係喺韓國買返香港的）<br />\n<br />\n巴打都可以學嚟冧女朋友（假如你有）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢應該會立即想嫁比你！"},{"pid":"028c44ebf35ecde073902be2d5c4af39152aeeee","tid":1034390,"uid":85984,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T00:31:31.000Z","msg":"睇過，咪公仔麵一個。有幾屈機呀"},{"pid":"14a5269259bce6a909aff5fa363cebe2528f24e2","tid":1034390,"uid":190818,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T00:34:21.000Z","msg":"韓國菜=即食加工食物<br />\n多謝巴打解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab324a2d9ce512f5d0c32d5150cb7c95ac15fc63","tid":1034390,"uid":186844,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T00:35:48.000Z","msg":"你老母睇落都好有誠意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2297554f5b9af51647bcab6acbbe51eabc94a61e","tid":1034390,"uid":4394,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T00:38:55.000Z","msg":"唔怪得鐘意追韓國野既都係智障多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77a2c14e23b025d651795bdb541d9cf45e476d5","tid":1034390,"uid":1713,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T00:40:49.000Z","msg":"韓國麵好垃圾"},{"pid":"e21318c762c75a13328b3ca67eb31ec31bbafb1e","tid":1034390,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T01:22:27.000Z","msg":"💖"},{"pid":"c838a9f62ebc40fb993fe7544e8dad89af4b552e","tid":1034390,"uid":90839,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T01:24:33.000Z","msg":"假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94aacea874fc842cbee638194308fbbd6422b15","tid":1034390,"uid":56999,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T01:58:38.000Z","msg":"七出之條  應該加多一條<br />\n<br />\n煮即食面當一餐者<br />\n可休"},{"pid":"6f137e73d834f27709d226a1ef59314faecd23b1","tid":1034390,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T02:15:24.000Z","msg":"韓國正宗部長鍋都無，嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829ee53895521314c72e1b6609a10b8f576a4741","tid":1034390,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T02:17:00.000Z","msg":"得一張心心圖咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6599ca1e9f48e8c2e524f571bdefd63d6b3b1d5e","tid":1034390,"uid":1399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T02:19:03.000Z","msg":"15妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />